_______________________________________________________________________________

         SAGA 4.2.0 - System for Automated Geoscientific Analyses
_______________________________________________________________________________

* Introduction

SAGA - System for Automated Geoscientific Analyses - is a Free Open Source Software for the analysis of spatial data.


* Internet

- www.saga-gis.org
- sourceforge.net/projects/saga-gis


* Supported Platforms

- Windows (Microsoft Visual C++ 10.0)
- Linux (gcc)
- FreeBSD


* Required Libraries

- wxWidgets 3.0.0
- GDAL 1.8.0
- Proj4
- Haru Free PDF Library (optional)
- libLAS 1.2 (optional)
- opencv (optional)
- vigra (optional)

